    "content": "We love receiving contributions, we're forever grateful for your help.\n\n## Overview\n\nHere are a few ways you can help improve Saas UI\n\n- **Improve the documentation**: Add new examples, fix typos, or add missing\n  information.\n- **Fix bugs**: Report bugs, fix bugs, or add missing features.\n- **Contribute to the code**: Propose new features by opening a Github\n  Discussion, or find existing bugs to work on.\n- **Improve the code**: Improve the code, fix bugs, or add missing features.\n\n## Architecture\n\nSaas v3.x is built on top of Chakra UI v3.x, and is a composition of two projects in the Chakra ecosystem, Ark UI and\nZag.js.\n\n- [Chakra UI](https://github.com/chakra-ui/chakra-ui) - The foundation of Saas UI\n- [Ark UI](https://github.com/chakra-ui/ark) - State machine from Zag.js converted to headless UI components\n- [Zag.js](https://github.com/chakra-ui/zag) - Component logic modelled as a state machine\n\n### Filing Issues\n\nBefore opening an issue, please check the following:\n\n- If the issue is a logic or accessibility bug, then it's most likely a bug in\n  Zag.js. Consider opening an issue in the Zag.js repository.\n\n- If it's a styling issue, then you can fix it directly in the Saas UI repo.\n\n### Feature Requests\n\nFeel free to open any feature requests, we'll review them to see if they're a good fit for Saas UI or if they should be implemented in Chakra UI or Zag.js.\n\n## Local Setup\n\n- Clone the repository\n\n```bash\ngit clone https://github.com/saas-ui/saas-ui.git\n```\n\n- Install dependencies\n\n```bash\nyarn\n```\n\n- Build local version of all packages\n\n```bash\nyarn build:packages\n```\n\n- Start storybook\n\n```bash\nyarn storybook\n```\n\n- Start documentation website\n\n```bash\nyarn dev:website\n```\n\n- Run tests\n\n```bash\nyarn test\n```\n\n## Recommended Extensions\n\nWe recommend using the following extensions in your editor:\n\n- [ESLint](https://eslint.org/)\n- [Prettier](https://prettier.io/)\n- [EditorConfig](https://editorconfig.org/)\n- [MDX](https://mdxjs.com/)",
