    "content": "Inspired by macOS and premium tools like Linear, Attio, and Superhuman, it provides intuitive primitives\nthat empower developers to create beautiful, user-friendly interfaces without sacrificing development velocity.\n\nWhether you're building a simple dashboard or a complex enterprise application, Saas UI helps you deliver polished experiences that users love.\n\n## Sponsors\n\n- [Frank Faubert](https://github.com/ffaubert)\n- [Appulse Software](https://appulse.net/)\n\n## Acknowledgements\n\nSaas UI is built with the help of many amazing libraries and their authors, without them this wouldn't be possible.\n\n- [Chakra UI](https://chakra-ui.com/) - The foundation of our components.\n- [React Hook Form](https://react-hook-form.com/) - Form state management.\n- [Tanstack Table](https://tanstack.com/table) - Basis of our DataGrid components.\n- [Shadcn UI](https://ui.shadcn.com/) - For the CLI",
